songs.title: Top 10 MC`s of all time :P?
songs.lyrics:
Whats ya guys top ten rappers of all time?
Mine is:
1. Eminem
2. Nas
3. Ice Cube
4. Jay Z
5. Dr. Dre
6. 50 Cent (I know he hasnt been in the best form lately, but overall he`s a great rapper)
7. Snoop D o dubble G
8. Biggie Smalls <3
9. 2Pac mane...
10. KanYe West ^^

This is about skills. Dre is my fav artist but he ain't the best rapper if we talk skills. But he make dem dope beats and best producer hands down. Comment your top 10 ;)
